snippet.textDisplay: Every coke studio season has a central theme music to it and this season is influenced by Rock bands such as AC/DC, Metallica and Guns n Roses which is no bigie because Noori initially was inspired by these very band. If you were expecting the same folk music rendition then you have 3 to 4 season worth of songs you can listen to again and again. But this is a season inspired by Rock and I am liking it and the one doesn't always have the option to wait for the next episode because I am sure there will be something for you. Not every song can be of your liking.
